other_tests.findings: Liver appears within normal limits, smooth contour, no focal liver mass, main portal vein patent with hepatopetal flow, no ascites. No intrahepatic biliary dilation, common hepatic duct measures 3 mm. No evidence of stones or gallbladder wall thickening. Pancreas not well visualized. Spleen normal echogenicity, measuring 9.3 cm. Right kidney measures 10.4 cm, left kidney measures 10.3 cm, no hydronephrosis seen.
